The 10th edition of the biggest and only local-based reggae concert, “Reggae in the Sun”, was held on Sunday at the Alliance Francaise in Nairobi. Three different bands will took to the stage. Among the artistes who performed at the event were first lady of hip hop Nazizi, who is best known for breaking ground in the hip hop scene in the early 2000s, reggae artiste Lavosti and Wen Music.